Server: Microsoft-IIS/5.0
Content-Type: text/html; charset=iso-8859-1
Content-Length: 33
WWW-Authenticate: NTLM TlRMTVNTUAACAAAACAAIADAAAAAGggEAq6U1NAWaJCIAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA4AAAATlRMTUF1dGg=

HTTP/1.1 401 Sorry wrong password
